
Precision medicine and drug development in Alzheimer's disease: the importance 
of sexual dimorphism and patient stratification.

Hampel H(1), Vergallo A(2), Giorgi FS(3), Kim SH(4), Depypere H(5), Graziani 
M(6), Saidi A(7), Nisticò R(8), Lista S(9); Alzheimer Precision Medicine 
