Incorporating Biomarkers into the Primary Prostate Biopsy Setting: A 
Cost-Effectiveness Analysis.

Sathianathen NJ(1), Kuntz KM(2), Alarid-Escudero F(2), Lawrentschuk NL(3), 
Bolton DM(4), Murphy DG(5), Weight CJ(6), Konety BR(6).

Author information:
